title: Dems start to get serious about 2020
content: **On the roster: - Time Out: ‘Since we're together, we might as well say…’ - Koch group boosts Heitkamp - Ryan running point on bid to block tariffs - Who has three thumbs and needs a lawyer? The Republican National Committee even ordered up a report memorializing those obvious conclusions. You would have to say former Vice President Joe Biden is the frontrunner if he really is serious about running.
